rComments: A real geek for the english language which is a plus because he does know his stuff.  Pretty down to earth but maintains the professor facade.  Don't regret taking his class.

nice guy, really slow and boring talker, always helpful but not much he needs to help with. Class is very simple and if you do the readings very interesting but if not then you might as well not show up because its useless for you to be there.

Slow when talking, you're going to get really bored and fall asleep. The class isn't hard but his marking is tough, even if you think you did an amazing essay, if he doesn't like it because it is too complicated for him, you will do bad. His way or no way he wants the essay dummed down, if you're in fourth year.. God help you.he wants simple essays
